This is a Hischip Intern Project.
The files consist of login.php,index.php,myfriends.php,logout.php

login.php ----
This file checks for the necessary login authorization information and logs in through the facebook login.
It implements facebook sdk and obtains the login url.

index.php ----
This file obtains the access token and prints the necessay user information that is name ,age,gender etc.
It also contains the buttons for friends list ang logging out.

myfriends.php ----
This prints the friends list.

logout.php ----
This logs out of the login.